<p>I have been working on a new project that combines knot theory with music.</p>
<section id="the-concept" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="the-concept">The Concept</h2>
<p>We are looking for a way to visualize the “interface” between geometric forms and organic forms.</p>
</section>
